                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7934" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1985</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1139 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">铸梦“世界薄板之王”：攀华集团全球价值链升级之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dream Casting “The King of the World Sheet” ：Panhua Group’s Global Value Chain Upgrading Journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘建徽，罗玮盛，刘小涵，高铭悦，李梦涵，张雪静，唐阳平，申欣怡，李璠，谢添赟，刘敏，周密</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">攀华集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">攀华集团；全球价值链；价值链升级；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Panhua Group; Global value chain; Value chain upgrading; Value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">推动我国制造业全球价值链水平由中低端向中高端攀升，是增强制造业价值创造水平与国际竞争力的迫切需要，也是实现我国经济高质量发展的战略选择。攀华集团在全球化的背景下，面对外部的机遇与挑战，是如何逐步实现全球价值链升级，发展成为我国薄板行业龙头企业的呢？本案例分三个阶段重点描述了攀华集团从成立之初抢占彩钢市场，成为中国民营企业最大的薄板生产基地之一；到抓住西部大开发战略机遇，专注科技创新、建立钢材市场、自建码头；再到通过与领先企业跨界合作，并“走出去”拓展海外市场，向“世界薄板之王”目标前进的全过程。本案例适用于《战略管理》《公司战略与风险管理》等课程，旨在引导学生充分认识全球价值链升级这一战略举措，帮助学生还原案例企业战略竞争优势的获取方式及其全球价值链升级的实现路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Promoting the level of global value chain of the Chinese manufacturing industry from the middle and low end to the middle and high end is an urgent need to enhance the value creation level and international competitiveness of manufacturing industry, and also a strategic choice to realize the high-quality development of Chinese economy. Under the background of globalization and facing external opportunities and challenges, how did Panhua Group gradually upgrade the global value chain and develop into a leading enterprise in Chinese thin plate industry? This case is divided into three stages, which mainly describes that Panhua Group seized the color steel market from the beginning of its establishment and became one of the largest thin plate production bases of private enterprises in China. To seize the strategic opportunity of western development, focus on scientific and technological innovation, establish steel market, and build its own wharf; Then, through cross-border cooperation with leading enterprises, and “going out” to expand overseas markets, the whole process of moving forward to the goal of “the king of thin plates in the world”. This case is suitable for courses such as Strategic Management, Corporate Strategy and Risk Management, aiming at guiding students to fully understand the strategic move of global value chain upgrading and helping students to restore the acquisition method of strategic competitive advantage of case enterprises and the realization path of global value chain upgrading.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业内外部环境分析；一体化战略；全球价值链升级；微笑曲线理论；OLI折衷理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
